Product Description:

This bag is made of superior genuine leather with cotton fabric lining inside, which made it wearable. It is nicely and neatly stitched to ensure its longevity. Its delicate design and workmanship makes you unique out of the crowds.

Material: genuine Italian cow leather; durable cotton fabric lining;

Size: approximately 13"L x 4.5"Wx 14.5"H inches (33cm L x 11.5cm W x 37cm H);

Color: red brown color;

Weight: approx. 0.9 KG;

String top closure;

This bag contains: 1*inside wallet pocket; 1*inside cell phone pocket; 1*compartment for laptop, files or documents.

Important notice!!! Please leave your full address and telephone/mobile phone number when placing the order, which are very important information for delivery.

